skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: good eats
des: Good Eats helps adults and minors to find out if particular food or food item is healthy or not. The data used in Good Eats is acquired from open contents and Good Eats services is not responsible for accuracy of the data. The answers, provided by Good Eats should not be used as rule or diet and common sense shall be always applied when following the answers that the application is providing. If you have special condition, you should consult with your doctor. Keep in mind that some food items that are healthy for one person, can be harmful for another (allergies, special diets, genetical and acquired diseases).
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
